{"tid":2303221,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"另一伴好似唔想公開...","createTime":"2020-11-27T17:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T07:52:23.000Z","uid":307793,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"42849af2489ff0aaaabdd3d6129facf69ccc906c","tid":2303221,"uid":307793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T17:55:54.000Z","msg":"我地一齊咗都係一兩個星期既事<br />\n曖昧曖昧下就一齊咗 <br />\n但係佢好似唔想比其他人知我地一齊<br />\n<br />\n我地係同事 咁係公司就會成日見架啦 <br />\n但佢係公司好似好避忌<br />\n唔知係咪我諗多咗啦<br />\n我地行埋一齊個陣 佢一見到有其他同事行過黎 佢就會即刻分開扮冇野 繼續做自己野 <br />\n都唔知話佢公私分明好定咩 但比我感覺唔多似<br />\n公司都有其他情侶 望番自己好似拍拖拍到地下情咁款<br />\n<br />\n話一齊個陣就好主動 一齊咗好似同冇一齊冇咩分別<br />\n出街拖個手都好似驚比熟人見到<br />\n<br />\n究竟係我諗多咗 定佢想穩定啲先公開<br />\n定佢真係唔想比人知我地拍緊拖<br />\nsor1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf63a0b54b3eda2ff39b2fe16b52f8350d66a1a","tid":2303221,"uid":7551,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T17:56:52.000Z","msg":"建議分手"},{"pid":"05409ea87654d2299d2a2b5677a7df0a099e8c06","tid":2303221,"uid":38904,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T17:57:57.000Z","msg":"感建分<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a423a1752d95baa4bddbcb1c6b01a187155691d6","tid":2303221,"uid":9392,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T18:01:18.000Z","msg":"哈 又一pair準備分手 開心～"},{"pid":"591f02a63ce0979eb19b12287b4cc0c3857c9d91","tid":2303221,"uid":219362,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T18:15:16.000Z","msg":"返工就返工啦<br />\n一陣工都冇得你做"},{"pid":"924c743c02247463a542e9a3719aa12a90b42ab2","tid":2303221,"uid":6145,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T18:21:53.000Z","msg":"返工就返工啦屌你"},{"pid":"a46cfbbda07b8eabbdabe9654fe26408e02fea87","tid":2303221,"uid":350206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T18:23:12.000Z","msg":"可能只係想低調？ <br />\n有冇帶你見朋友吖？"},{"pid":"c5ac92f9decda1d5ee503090c566706fd0c2e82e","t